Once upon a Time in a forest their lived a monkey named JAggu
who resided on a jamun Tree,WHich was on a bank in a river , 
in the same forest their lived a Crocodile named Ghatak and his wife Mani
 One fine day Ghatak came to the bank of the river and rested under the jamun Tree
 the kind-hearted JAggu offered him some fruit.
 the Ghatak came back the next day asking for more fruits as he loved them 
 in this way JAggu and Ghatak became good friends
